<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Excellent Hotel My family and I had to spend a night in Mexico City en-route to SF from Mazatlan this past weekend and we were very much suprised by the accomodation at this hotel. It is a very modern and beautiful building. They have a shuttle at Gate 4 or 6 in Terminal A off the airport which runs 24 hours a day every hour on the hour. We checked in around 8:00PM and had dinner at the buffet in the restaurant on-site and it was very delicious. The room is spacious and comes with all of the modern amenities including free Internet Access. The bed is little stiff for my taste but other than that it was a very pleasant stay. We may spend a few days in Mexico City for sightseiing the next time we come to visit. 
