<Author>parsley4733
<Content>Beautiful Hotel We stayed one night at this Hotel after arriving late one night in Dec 2003. This hotel is a 70's style hotel but absoulutely a must see and a walk thru all open levels can be breathtaking. Lots of Dali artwork thruout and open views to outside. Rooms are large and clean. There is a restaraunt in the hotel. Food is good and service was good. Not many accesible restaraunts close by. There is an airport shuttle which we found in the National part of the airport. Look for a person holding sign with name of hotel. You can discuss price and fix price with person there before you go to hotel. 
